    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Portraits of the donors of a work, depicted in the work depicting a narrative or other scene. The donors may be depicted as themselves, or they may take on the character of one of the actors in the narrative. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
